## Opis

Blue Team Operations Center je enterprise-grade platforma za izvajanje defenzivnih varnostnih operacij, vključno s SIEM/SOC monitoring, threat detection, incident response, forensic analysis in threat hunting.

## Vključene komponente

### SIEM/SOC Monitoring
- Log aggregation
- Event correlation
- Real-time alerting
- Dashboard visualization
- Compliance reporting

### Threat Detection
- Signature-based detection
- Behavioral analysis
- Anomaly detection
- Machine learning detection
- MITRE ATT&CK mapping

### Incident Response
- Incident triage
- Containment procedures
- Eradication steps
- Recovery processes
- Post-incident review

### Forensic Analysis
- Evidence collection
- Timeline analysis
- Artifact examination
- Chain of custody
- Court-ready reporting

### Threat Hunting
- Hypothesis-driven hunting
- IOC-based hunting
- Behavioral hunting
- Proactive threat discovery
- Hunt playbooks

### Vulnerability Management
- Asset discovery
- Vulnerability scanning
- Risk prioritization
- Patch management
- Remediation tracking

